INUMBER 1317
NAME 906
ARTICLE SOME
WEIGHT 1000
VOLUME 1000
INTERIOR 3
CONTAINER IN
IFPREVERB GO -1
        CLEARVERB
        ECHO PLAYER You sit down on the grass.
        ECHO OTHERS %N sits down on the grass.
        POSITION SIT
ENDIF
IFPREVERB KICK -1
        CLEARVERB
        ECHO PLAYER You scuff your feet on the grass.
        ECHO OTHERS %N scuffs %h feet on the grass.
ENDIF
HIDDEN

;
;

NUMBER 3189
NAME Entombed!
OUTOFBODY
DEEPCAVE
DARKNESS
CHANNEL 84
REGION 4
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
You are entombed in a magical bed of solid rock. Much of your power, many of
your memories and even parts of your identity are lost here... all you can do
is dig your way out, ever so slowly...
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB DIG -1
        CLEARVERB
        POSITION STAND
        ECHO PLAYER You actually have to focus all of your concentration on going UP to get out of here...
ENDIF

IFPREVERB UP -1
        CLEARVERB
        ECHO PLAYER You struggle to force your way out, getting a little closer...
        ADD FLAG1 STR
        IFVAR FLAG1 < 1000
                ECHO PLAYER [Round: 10 sec]
                EQUAL ROUNDTIME 10
        ENDIF
        IFVAR FLAG1 > 999
                ECHO PLAYER You've made it, clawing your way up out of the ground...
                AFFECT INTNUM11
                ECHO OTHERS %N claws %h way up out of the ground!
                AFFECT 3189
                MOVE INTNUM11
        ENDIF
ENDIF

;
;

INUMBER 994
NAME 864
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 4
*DESCRIPTION_START
The carvings on the headstone are in an unknown language, but the pictoral
ones seem to show someone praying and wielding it like a shield against a
hideous, otherwordly attacker.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB WIELD -1
        CLEARVERB
        EQUAL ITEMVAL1 0
        IFVAR REGION ! 0
                IFVAR REGION ! 4
                        ECHO PLAYER You can't seem to get a grip on it here.
                        EQUAL ITEMVAL1 1
                ENDIF
        ENDIF
        IFVAR ITEMVAL1 = 0
                IFVAR TERRAIN > 11
                        ECHO PLAYER You can't seem to get a grip on it here.
                        EQUAL ITEMVAL1 1
                ENDIF
        ENDIF
        IFVAR ITEMVAL1 = 0
                ECHO PLAYER As you begin to brandish the headstone skeletal hands reach up from the ground and pull you under! You are clawed and dragged down, down...
                DAMAGEPLR SLASH 10 One hand manages to do some damage to you.
                ECHO OTHERS Skeletal hands reach up and grab %n, pulling %i, screaming, into the ground!
                EQUAL INTNUM11 RNUM
                MOVE 3189
        ENDIF
ENDIF

